<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَإِلَيْنَا تُرْجَعُونَ}</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٦ - <span class="c3">{وَإِذَا رَآكَ الَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا إِنْ يَتَّخِذُونَكَ}</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(ما يتخذونك)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{إِلَّا هُزُوًا}</span> سخريًا يقول بعضهم لبعض <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c3">{أَهَذَا الَّذِي يَذْكُرُ آلِهَتَكُمْ}</span> بسوء ويعيبها <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قال عنترة:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>لا تذكري مهري وما أطعمته ... فيكون جلدك مثل جلد الأجرب <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">أي:</span> لا تعيبي مهري.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>* * *<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
